{
  "stem": "4284.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "We were forced to go to Weimar, which was the nearest city down the hill, to clean up the rubble of the destruction of the city.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "And that's the only clue we had that obviously, you know, there's still bombing going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 106,
      "text": "But the camp itself wasn't bombed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 107,
      "text": "At previous time before I had arrived, it was, because they were making bullets there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 108,
      "text": "But that had ceased because the factory was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 109,
      "text": "So we lingered around, other than going down to Weimar, basically with the hope that in the rubble, you might find some extra food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 110,
      "text": "The work was excruciating, because it was 10, 12 hours a day then to transport back up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 111,
      "text": "And all of the sudden, things got kind of quiet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 112,
      "text": "And for 11 days, 10 or 11 days, no food, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 113,
      "text": "All of us were now much too weak.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 114,
      "text": "Tremendous death rate of people with this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 115,
      "text": "For whatever reason, the younger inmates had a little bit more life-sustaining strength.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 116,
      "text": "We all had a great deal of hope.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 117,
      "text": "And one day while we were laying around, since you couldn't move you were so weak, we hear strange noises and some yelling.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 118,
      "text": "And we thought for sure the Germans are now eradicating this whole camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 119,
      "text": "You hear some shots, you hear some-- but you hear some joyous-- it wasn't anger, fear, panic, didn't know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 120,
      "text": "We raised ourselves up and climbed up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 121,
      "text": "The, the Germans did take potshots at us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 122,
      "text": "But that's what we thought.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 123,
      "text": "We looked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 124,
      "text": "And the first thing somebody said, and we thought he was a hallucinating, there was a tank facing, coming through the building with a Star of David on it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 125,
      "text": "Well, you figure, you know, that somebody has lost it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 126,
      "text": "We looked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 127,
      "text": "And that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
